  <brief_title>Single vs Double Epidural Catheter Analgesia for Scoliosis Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Single Versus Double Epidural Catheter Technique for Postoperative Analgesia Following Scoliosis Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
